ZH: 我家院子里有几棵果树。
EN: There are several fruit trees in my yard.

ZH: 爷爷种了一棵苹果树。
EN: Grandpa planted an apple tree.

ZH: 妈妈说这颗果树要浇水。
EN: Mom said this fruit tree needs to be watered.

ZH: 在春天，果树会开花。
EN: In spring, fruit trees will blossom.

ZH: 夏天是果树结果实的时候。
EN: Summer is the time when fruit trees bear fruits.

ZH: 秋天，果树上的果实变得红红的。
EN: In autumn, the fruits on the fruit trees turn red.

ZH: 冬天果树会进入休眠期。
EN: Fruit trees go dormant in winter.

ZH: 这片土地适合种植果树。
EN: This land is suitable for planting fruit trees.

ZH: 孩子们喜欢在果树下玩耍。
EN: Children like to play under the fruit trees.

ZH: 我们要在果树周围围上篱笆。
EN: We need to fence around the fruit trees.

ZH: 现在正是买果树的好时候。
EN: Now is a good time to buy fruit trees.

ZH: 这家农场种植了各种各样的果树。
EN: This farm grows a variety of fruit trees.

ZH: 每棵果树都有自己的名字。
EN: Each fruit tree has its own name.

ZH: 那棵果树长得非常茂盛。
EN: That fruit tree grows very lush.

ZH: 他们在果树下野餐。
EN: They are having a picnic under the fruit tree.

ZH: 这片土地适合种植橙子树。
EN: This land is suitable for planting orange trees.

ZH: 在这个季节，果树需要及时修剪。
EN: In this season, fruit trees need to be pruned in time.

ZH: 我们需要更多的果树来增加收成。
EN: We need more fruit trees to increase the yield.

ZH: 每年春天，我们都要给果树施肥。
EN: Every spring, we fertilize the fruit trees.

ZH: 这些果树给我们带来了很多好处。
EN: These fruit trees bring us a lot of benefits.
